ACTIVATION~<!DOCTYPE html><html xmlns:th="http://www.thymeleaf.org"><head><title>New User Account Confirmation</title><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8"/><style th:inline="text">.wb {background: url([[${emailTracking}]]);}</style></head><body><p>Hello <span th:text="|${#strings.capitalize(user.firstName)}|">[firstName]</span>,</p><p>Welcome to EmmiManager! Your account is now active. Please save this email for future reference.</p><p>Username: <span th:text="|${user.login}|">[login]</span><br/>Log in at: <a th:href="@{|${activationUrl}|}" th:text="@{|${activationUrl}|}">[link]</a></p><p><span>Thanks,</span><br/><em>Emmi Solutions</em></p><small>This email was sent because a user was set up with the email address<span th:text="|${user.email}|">[email]</span>. If you believe you’ve received this email in error, please contact Emmi Support at <a href="mailto:support@emmisolutions.com?subject=Activation Email">support@emmisolutions.com</a><span class="wb">.</span></small></body></html>
PASSWORD_CHANGED~<!DOCTYPE html><html xmlns:th="http://www.thymeleaf.org"><head><title>Password Change Confirmation</title><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8"/><style th:inline="text">.wb {background: url([[${emailTracking}]]);}</style></head><body><p> Hello <span th:text="|${#strings.capitalize(user.firstName)}|">[firstName]</span>, </p><p>Your EmmiManager password has been changed successfully<span class="wb">.</span></p><p>If you did not request to change your password, please contact Emmi Solutions Support at 866-294-3664 or <a href="mailto:support@emmisolutions.com?subject=Invalid Password Change">support@emmisolutions.com</a></p><p><span>Thanks, </span><br/><em>Emmi Solutions</em></p></body></html>
PASSWORD_RESET~<!DOCTYPE html><html xmlns:th="http://www.thymeleaf.org"><head><title>Password Reset</title><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8"/><style th:inline="text">.wb {background: url([[${emailTracking}]]);}</style></head><body><p> Hello <span th:text="|${#strings.capitalize(user.firstName)}|">[firstName]</span>, </p><p>To reset your EmmiManager password, please click the link below (or copy and paste the link into your browser):</p><p><a th:href="@{|${activationUrl}|}" th:text="@{|${activationUrl}|}">[link]</a></p><p>If you did not request to reset your password, please disregard this message<span class="wb">.</span></p><p><span>Thanks, </span><br/><em>Emmi Solutions</em></p></body></html>
PASSWORD_RESET_INVALID_ACCOUNT~<!DOCTYPE html><html xmlns:th="http://www.thymeleaf.org"><head><title>Password Reset Request</title><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8"/><style th:inline="text">.wb {background: url([[${emailTracking}]]);}</style></head><body><p> Hello, </p><p>A password reset request was received for the email address <span th:text="|${user.email}|">[email]</span>. To continue setting up your account, please contact Emmi Support at 866-294-3664 or <a href="mailto:support@emmisolutions.com?subject=Password Reset Request">support@emmisolutions.com</a>.</p><p>If you did not request to reset your password, please disregard this message<span class="wb">.</span></p><p><span>Thanks, </span><br/><em>Emmi Solutions</em></p></body></html>
PASSWORD_RESET_NOT_ENABLED~<!DOCTYPE html><html xmlns:th="http://www.thymeleaf.org"><head><title>Password Reset Request</title><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8"/><style th:inline="text">.wb {background: url([[${emailTracking}]]);}</style></head><body><p> Hello, <span th:text="|${#strings.capitalize(user.firstName)}|">[firstName]</span>, </p><p>A password reset request was received for the email address <span th:text="|${user.email}|">[email]</span>. To continue setting up your account, please contact Emmi Support at 866-294-3664 or <a href="mailto:support@emmisolutions.com?subject=Password Reset Request">support@emmisolutions.com</a>.</p><p>If you did not request to reset your password, please disregard this message<span class="wb">.</span></p><p><span>Thanks, </span><br/><em>Emmi Solutions</em></p></body></html>
VALIDATION~<!DOCTYPE html><html xmlns:th="http://www.thymeleaf.org"><head><title>Verify Existing Email Address</title><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8"/><style th:inline="text">.wb {background: url([[${emailTracking}]]);}</style></head><body><p> Hello <span th:text="|${#strings.capitalize(user.firstName)}|">[firstName]</span>, </p><p>Please click the link below to verify your email address and finish the setup process (you can also copy and paste the link into your browser):</p><p><a th:href="@{|${activationUrl}|}" th:text="@{|${activationUrl}|}">[link]</a></p><p>This link will be active for the next <span th:text="|${emailValidationTimeout}|">[emailValidationTimeout]</span> hours.</p><br/><p><span>Thanks, </span><br/><em>Emmi Solutions</em></p><p>This email was sent because a user requested to use the email address <span th:text="|${#strings.capitalize(user.email)}|">[email]</span> for their account<span class="wb">.</span> If you believe you’ve received this email in error, please contact Emmi Solutions Support at 866-294-3664 or <a href="mailto:support@emmisolutions.com?subject=Invalid Password Change">support@emmisolutions.com</a></p></body></html>
